## intellij actions keymap
# action + ?
nnoremap <Space>arc :action ReformatCode<CR>
nnoremap <Space>arf :action Refactorings.QuickListPopupAction<CR>
nnoremap <Space>aia :action ShowIntentionActions<CR>
nnoremap <Space>asw :action SurroundWith<CR>
nnoremap <Space>aoi :action OptimizeImports<CR>

# fold
nnoremap <Space>fca :action CollapseAllRegions<CR>
nnoremap <Space>fea :action ExpandAllRegions<CR>



nnoremap <M-k> :action MoveLineUp<CR>
nnoremap <M-j> :action MoveLineDown<CR>


